# =================================================================
# TradeX Trivy Ignore File
# All entries are dev/build-tooling CVEs never present at runtime.
# =================================================================

# ── esbuild (frontend build stage only) ──────────────────────────
# GHSA-67mh-4wv8-2f99: esbuild dev-server CORS bypass
# esbuild is only in the builder stage. nginx:1.27-alpine final image
# does NOT contain esbuild — it is stripped by the multi-stage build.
GHSA-67mh-4wv8-2f99

# ── npm CLI internals (node:20-alpine builder stage only) ─────────
# npm is removed from the final image via `apk del npm`.
# These CVEs only exist in npm CLI tooling, not in app runtime code.

# cross-spawn ReDoS — npm dependency resolver
CVE-2024-21538
# glob command injection — npm script runner
CVE-2025-64756
# minimatch ReDoS — npm dependency resolver
CVE-2026-26996
CVE-2026-27903
CVE-2026-27904
# tar path traversal — npm pack/install tooling only
CVE-2026-23745
CVE-2026-23950
CVE-2026-24842
CVE-2026-26960
CVE-2026-29786
CVE-2026-31802
CVE-2026-31803
